item.description:
Let's start off 2011 with a plan. Join us tonight as we formulate our business strategy for 2011! Maureen will share tips and strategies to keep you on track straight through until 2012!

Don't forget to bring your business cards and materials to share with others.
item.how_to_find_us: Parking is available across the street in the business complex and requires a short walk to the business location.
